Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:00.53,0:00:04.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,櫻花綻放之未來戀夢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:14.48,0:00:20.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,天空好藍 你露出了微笑
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:22.25,0:00:28.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不經意的一句話使內心相繫
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:29.26,0:00:35.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,剛穿上的鞋  敞開門扉的後方
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:37.03,0:00:43.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,跟你重合的景色使我心動
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:46.98,0:00:54.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,櫻花綻放之未來戀夢\N加速的心跳無法壓抑
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:54.88,0:01:02.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,兩人共同感受  季節不斷更替
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:02.39,0:01:10.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,無可取代的瞬間\N編織著邂逅的物語
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:10.40,0:01:17.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,對紛飛的櫻花許下心願
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:17.41,0:01:19.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,向前行
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:21.24,0:01:23.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,花盛開著
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:30.05,0:01:32.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,（#18 只屬於兩人的祕密）
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:34.72,0:01:35.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,音夢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:39.96,0:01:40.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,音夢…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:03.61,0:03:05.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,雙親因車禍亡故的音夢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:06.88,0:03:08.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,小時候就被我們家收養
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:13.45,0:03:14.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,音夢？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:18.79,0:03:21.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,她總是會注意週遭人們的臉色
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:22.63,0:03:25.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,感覺像是沒有她容身之處
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:30.14,0:03:33.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這樣的她有一天離家出走了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:55.33,0:03:56.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,音夢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:07.24,0:04:10.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那傢伙跑到哪裡去了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:46.51,0:04:47.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,音夢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:54.46,0:04:56.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,早安，哥哥
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:58.53,0:05:01.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,妳從昨天就一直在這裡嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:15.61,0:05:18.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好舒服，現在是早春呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:21.48,0:05:23.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你知道嗎，哥哥
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:25.35,0:05:28.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,只要在這棵櫻花樹下許願
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:29.56,0:05:31.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,願望就一定可以實現
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:33.36,0:05:35.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,妳竟然還能說得這麼悠閒
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:35.80,0:05:37.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,大家都很擔心妳呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:39.30,0:05:43.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,月光照在樹上看起來好像人影
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:43.57,0:05:48.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,風吹樹葉的沙沙聲\N好像有人在走路，害我好怕
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:49.28,0:05:50.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,遠方有狗在叫
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:52.15,0:05:54.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,晚上又好冷
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:57.39,0:06:00.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好害怕，我真的好害怕
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:01.39,0:06:05.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,所以我希望哥哥能來救我
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:07.16,0:06:12.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,一直在跟櫻花樹許願
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:15.47,0:06:17.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那又何必要離家出走呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:18.84,0:06:23.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,因為有我在只會給哥哥添麻煩
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:25.35,0:06:31.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,也給哥哥的爸媽添麻煩
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:32.42,0:06:34.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我一直是個愛哭鬼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:35.92,0:06:38.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,所以沒有我會比較好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:43.26,0:06:45.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,別讓我擔心啦，笨蛋
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:51.01,0:06:52.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,別想那麼多啦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:53.01,0:06:55.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,就算妳失敗了我也會想辦法
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:56.14,0:06:58.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,妳被人欺負我就去打回來
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:59.58,0:07:02.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,有不愛吃的東西我就幫妳吃
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:03.72,0:07:05.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,發生什麼事情我都會幫妳
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:06.79,0:07:08.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,妳是我的妹妹
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:09.72,0:07:10.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我會保護妳
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:12.23,0:07:13.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我永遠都是妳的哥哥
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:16.66,0:07:17.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,哥哥
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:26.04,0:07:28.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,小小的她一直在煩惱
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:29.81,0:07:31.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,一直在跟孤獨搏鬥
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:32.68,0:07:35.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我好氣自己竟然沒發覺
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:37.99,0:07:41.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那時起我就發誓要保護音夢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:44.93,0:07:46.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,無論如何都要保護她
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:48.56,0:07:49.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,以哥哥的身份…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:57.07,0:08:02.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,從那天起我就一直告訴自己\N我跟音夢是兄妹
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:03.78,0:08:04.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,一直…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:08.78,0:08:09.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真是累人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:16.46,0:08:17.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,賴子？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:18.96,0:08:20.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,哥哥
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:22.03,0:08:22.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,音夢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:24.87,0:08:27.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那個…我肚子餓了…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:30.30,0:08:32.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我也是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:40.58,0:08:41.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,對不起
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:43.78,0:08:45.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,存糧都沒了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:47.56,0:08:48.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,沒關係啦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:53.46,0:08:56.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,盯著看沒辦法變成兩碗嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:05.44,0:09:07.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,哥哥你先吃
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:10.21,0:09:13.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不，還是音夢妳先吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:15.48,0:09:16.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我真的沒關係
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:35.00,0:09:38.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,沒吃飽肚子反而更餓
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:39.57,0:09:40.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,的確是呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:47.01,0:09:47.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,要吃嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:49.98,0:09:51.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,妳討厭吃和果子對吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:56.29,0:09:57.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,並不是討厭
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:58.39,0:10:00.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我只是假裝討厭
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:01.13,0:10:02.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,假裝討厭？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:03.60,0:10:06.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我知道哥哥會變和果子出來
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:09.04,0:10:09.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,其實我很喜歡吃
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:11.14,0:10:13.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,可是我一直在逞強
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:14.81,0:10:16.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,逞強？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:16.14,0:10:21.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,小櫻每次都會纏著哥哥\N變和果子給她吃對吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:25.45,0:10:26.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,哥哥
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:31.69,0:10:32.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,妳看
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:38.83,0:10:42.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我所不知道的哥哥祕密\N竟然只有小櫻知道
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:47.94,0:10:49.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我好羨慕小櫻
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:50.71,0:10:52.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,所以我才討厭和果子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:09.80,0:11:10.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,所以…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:20.61,0:11:22.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,如果我什麼都不做
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:22.21,0:11:25.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,哥哥又會跟那時一樣被搶走了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:25.85,0:11:28.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,小櫻就會把哥哥搶走了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:30.02,0:11:31.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,音夢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:33.22,0:11:34.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼是小櫻呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:36.36,0:11:37.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,只有小櫻我不接受
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:46.37,0:11:49.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,哥哥，我在等你喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:50.84,0:11:52.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,都是哥哥不對
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:53.24,0:11:53.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,哥哥…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:55.74,0:11:57.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,都是哥哥…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:57.28,0:11:59.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,音夢，妳怎麼了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:00.65,0:12:01.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,妳發燒了嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:02.65,0:12:04.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,妳累了，今天趕快睡吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:04.89,0:12:06.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我一點也不累啦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:07.66,0:12:09.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,哥哥真是奸詐
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:09.36,0:12:11.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,每次都這樣轉移話題
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:11.49,0:12:14.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,察覺我想表達心意時就躲開
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:14.43,0:12:16.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,回答我，哥哥
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:16.40,0:12:17.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:17.90,0:12:19.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:19.57,0:12:21.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我真的好喜歡哥哥
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:29.44,0:12:30.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我察覺到了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:32.18,0:12:35.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,早上起床音夢的眼神就在看我
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:36.02,0:12:38.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,每次下課時都會轉身注意我
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:40.45,0:12:44.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,每次說完晚安後\N總是欲言又止的嘴唇
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:46.66,0:12:49.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,音夢總是在注意著我
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:53.43,0:12:54.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我早就察覺到了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:55.57,0:12:57.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,所以才會假裝不知道
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:59.94,0:13:04.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我不想因為發現音夢的心意\N而破壞兩人的關係
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:06.08,0:13:07.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,破壞名為兄妹的關係
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:10.68,0:13:14.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,因為從那天起我就告訴自己\N我要永遠保護音夢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:15.92,0:13:19.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,所以我也封閉了自己的心意
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:19.46,0:13:21.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,哥哥…你太奸詐了啦…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:23.20,0:13:24.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,的確很奸詐
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:25.13,0:13:27.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,明明察覺到卻不敢採取行動
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:28.37,0:13:30.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,哥哥是笨蛋
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:33.34,0:13:34.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我的確是個笨蛋
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:41.85,0:13:42.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,笨蛋
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:43.75,0:13:45.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,哥哥是個大笨蛋…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:48.32,0:13:50.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我真的是個大笨蛋
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:07.14,0:14:07.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我好高興
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:09.88,0:14:10.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,哥哥…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:19.89,0:14:21.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,醒來的時候很清爽
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:22.39,0:14:23.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,可是我卻動不了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:25.13,0:14:26.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,只要想到昨天的自己…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:31.17,0:14:32.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我不管了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:35.20,0:14:36.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,總覺得會不好意思
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:37.40,0:14:40.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,要舉例的話就像是\N日記被看到時的難為情
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:41.54,0:14:43.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不過我沒有寫就是了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:46.21,0:14:48.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,跟二流電影一樣只是場夢嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:53.45,0:14:54.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這是留在現實中的證據
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:57.19,0:14:58.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,早安
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:00.33,0:15:02.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,早安，哥哥
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:04.90,0:15:05.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,早安
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:08.60,0:15:11.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那應該不是夢吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:14.48,0:15:15.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那不是夢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:17.21,0:15:20.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這麼說害我不好意思到\N很想對自己吐槽
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:23.32,0:15:26.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,天空的藍以及風的味道
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:26.22,0:15:29.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,眼中的一切都跟昨天不同
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:31.49,0:15:34.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,櫻花的香味也比平常明顯
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:35.86,0:15:37.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,感覺充滿了整個鼻腔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:39.73,0:15:42.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,從昨天到今天改變最多的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:43.87,0:15:45.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,則是我和音夢之間的關係
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:56.72,0:15:59.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我忘不了櫻花飛舞的這一天吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:01.22,0:16:03.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,彼此印證內心真正的感情
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:05.09,0:16:07.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,踏出嶄新一步的這一天
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:09.60,0:16:12.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,哥哥，快點啦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:12.53,0:16:13.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,電影要開始囉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:20.24,0:16:21.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真是累人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:30.02,0:16:31.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,預告
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:31.15,0:16:33.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這下可真是累人囉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:33.15,0:16:35.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,竟然又說這種話
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:35.79,0:16:36.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,哥哥真愛欺負人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:37.99,0:16:42.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,可是我們以後會怎麼樣呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:43.43,0:16:45.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這份感情已經停不下來了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:45.57,0:16:47.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,就任其發展下去吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:47.84,0:16:49.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,妳說對吧，音夢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:50.00,0:16:50.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,哥哥
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:52.04,0:16:54.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,太幸福到讓我好害怕呢\N（#19 幸福的時間）
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:08.96,0:17:16.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,蒐集心的碎片  想趕快送給你
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:16.53,0:17:21.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,似乎快要滿溢  真是不可思議
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:23.27,0:17:26.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,鈴音輕響
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:26.94,0:17:31.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,兩人漫步於樹林小道
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:31.98,0:17:34.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,合而為一的影子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:34.45,0:17:40.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,高興地凝視著夕陽
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:43.22,0:17:46.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,櫻花之雨在飛舞
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:47.03,0:17:50.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,由樹梢陽光所籠罩
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:50.76,0:17:59.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,現在累積於胸口的哀傷啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:59.17,0:18:06.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,更替的季節與不變的笑容
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:06.35,0:18:14.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,一定會演奏通往未來的旋律
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:14.56,0:18:20.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,閉上眼睛也能見到你
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:22.66,0:18:23.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,永遠都能在一起
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:36.80,0:20:37.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼了嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:40.20,0:20:41.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,（啊？）
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:43.57,0:20:44.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼突然這樣呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:49.24,0:20:52.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我臉上有什麼東西嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:08.79,0:21:10.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼了嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:10.46,0:21:12.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,感覺上跟平常不太一樣
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:15.03,0:21:17.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,（不、沒什麼）
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:17.30,0:21:19.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,奇怪，果然很奇怪
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:21.61,0:21:22.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你今天很奇怪喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:24.61,0:21:26.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你看過萬國博覽會對吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:27.88,0:21:30.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真好，有展示月球的石頭對吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:33.49,0:21:35.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我也好想去月亮看看呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:37.72,0:21:42.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這一步是我的一小步
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:42.29,0:21:45.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,卻是人類的一大步
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:47.30,0:21:50.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,太空人阿姆斯壯好帥呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:55.41,0:21:56.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,來
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:03.82,0:22:04.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,來吃吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:06.75,0:22:10.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,對了，我昨天買了張迷你搖滾
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:10.42,0:22:11.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,下次要不要來聽呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:14.09,0:22:17.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,短暫的日子中\N剛選上議員就被處分
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:17.36,0:22:19.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,希望藉著辭職激起一陣漣漪
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:21.10,0:22:22.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你是看過這個廣告才買的吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:22.84,0:22:24.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,下次借我看一下吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:24.34,0:22:26.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不知道阿徹的比賽結果怎麼樣
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:29.27,0:22:31.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你知道澤木同學家嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:31.61,0:22:33.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,聽說他們買了彩色電視呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:35.18,0:22:36.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,很棒對吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:36.62,0:22:39.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這可是島上第一台彩色電視喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:39.69,0:22:42.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我也好想看，真的很漂亮吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:48.13,0:22:49.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你這樣不行啦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:50.43,0:22:51.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼了嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:52.06,0:22:54.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,跟平常的你不一樣呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:56.64,0:22:57.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,芳乃
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:58.64,0:23:01.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,白河，妳什麼時候回來的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:02.31,0:23:03.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我早上剛到
